root: ^We've still got a bit of work left to do here before the level rework is playable.
^That said, The layout changes are almost all here. Feel free to look around.
^Any red block is supposed to denote a blockade of some sort,
^so just imagine there's a bunch of destroyed crap in the way when you see those.
^At the time of writing, the graveyard is yet to be reworked, but the rest of the level is pretty much there.
